<item>
 <title>VILAS INTRODUCATION</title>
 <link>http://boa.gov.vn/en/vilas-introducation</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dichvu-phamvi field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-dich-vu-noi-dung-bai-viet field-type-text-long field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;THE VIETNAM LABORATORY ACCREDITATION SCHEME (VILAS)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Vietnam Laboratory Accreditation Scheme (VILAS) is one of accreditation schemes of BoA:&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Organization and operation conform with the requirements of ISO/IEC 17011:2004&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Assessment criteria: ISO/IEC 17025:2005 and supplementary requirements for each specific scope&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Full member and signatory of Mutual Recognition Arrangement with&amp;nbsp;&lt;br /&gt;
o&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Asia Pacific Laboratory Accreditation Cooperation (APLAC)&lt;br /&gt;
o&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;International Laboratory Accreditation Cooperation (ILAC)&lt;br /&gt;
Up to now, over 900 laboratories have been accredited.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;Benefit of Laboratory Accreditation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To upgraded the competence of laboratory on &amp;nbsp;technical and management aspects&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To ensure the correctness and reliability of testing/calibration&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To facilitate the recognition of testing/calibration results&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;To integrate the laboratory accreditation activities of Vietnam with those of regional and international countries.&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;The Accreditation Field&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Mechanical&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Chemical&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Biological&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Pharmaceutical&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Electrical – Electronic&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Civil Engineering&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Non-Destruction testing&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Measurement and Calibration&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Biosafety&lt;br /&gt;
•&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &amp;nbsp;Medical&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field-name-field-makup-chia-se field-type-markup field-label-hidden&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field-item even&quot;&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
